                        <h2>Our Events</h2>
                        <p>_____</p>
                        <p> We sell our nutrient dense, raw, vegan products at the Shreveport Farmer’s Market, as well as local festivals, venues and shops. Sacred Strawberry also offers wild edible consultations.  We will come to your garden and tell you what you have growing, how you could optimize certain plants in your garden, as well as how to prepare and use the plants we find.  We lead free wild plant walks, so come along on one of those!</p>
