                        <h2>Inspiration</h2>
                        <p>_____</p>
                        <p>Sacred Strawberry Raw Organic Treats is a family affair based in Shreveport, Louisiana. Owned and run by Emily and Daniel Mills, the husband and wife duo decided to offer something different and from the heart to the local community after living abroad for 8 years.Emily has been experimenting with and learning about raw foods from some of the biggest names in in the raw food movement, such as Dr. Gabriel Cousens and Kate Magic for over 6 years and feels a deep calling to share healthy food for vibrant living!.</p>

